    "image_tabs_zr9wQH": {
      "type": "image-tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "tab_7Vt2kL": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Precision Progress in a Compact Design",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Precision_Progress_in_a_Compact_Design.webp",
            "text": "<p>Precision Progress in a Compact Design<br/>Progressive overload is the foundation of muscle growth. Large 10 lb jumps can stall progress or increase injury risk.<br/>Our adjustable dumbbells set offers:</p><ul><li>Up to 12 multiple micro-adjustment levels</li><li>Smooth dial-based weight selection</li><li>Compact frame that preserves full range of motion</li></ul><p>This makes Ativafit adjustable dumbbells ideal for controlled progression, hypertrophy training, and joint-friendly workouts.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_9Qe4mR": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Real Steel Feel vs. Bulky Plastic",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Real_Steel_Feel_vs._Bulky_Plastic.webp",
            "text": "<p>Many adjustable weight dumbbells rely heavily on plastic parts, which can feel unbalanced or wear out over time.<br/>Ativafit adjustable dumbbells set prioritizes solid steel plates and metal internal dials, delivering:</p><ul><li>Dense, balanced feel like traditional dumbbells</li><li>Secure internal locking system</li><li>Long-term durability for heavy training</li></ul><p><br/>This is not just adjustable convenience. It is professional-grade performance in a compact design.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_R4p2aN": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Engineered for Lifetime Stability",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/dumbbell_feature.webp",
            "text": "<p>Many budget brands use thin single-layer trays that shift during racking.<br/>Ativafit adjustable dumbbell sets are built for durability with:</p><ul><li>Reinforced dual-layer base</li><li>Secure docking system</li><li>Replaceable parts for long-term ownership</li></ul><p>Your home gym stays stable, quiet, and professional, workout after workout.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_1dK3s8": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Empower Every Family Member",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Empower_Every_Family_Member.webp",
            "text": "<p>From 27.5 lb beginner models to 88 lb heavy-duty adjustable weights, Ativafit adjustable dumbbells are built to grow with your strength.</p><ul><li>Beginners starting strength training</li><li>Couples sharing a home gym</li><li>Experienced lifters pushing heavier loads<br/><br/>Instead of buying multiple fixed dumbbells, one adjustable dumbbell set grows with every family member.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "tab_7Vt2kL",
